@startuml poc_sequence
title OpenSDLC PoC — 실행 시퀀스 다이어그램\n(poc_classic.yaml 기준: ReqAgent → ValidatorAgent → CodeAgent)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  ActorBorderColor #2980B9
  LifeLineBorderColor #7F8C8D
  ParticipantBorderColor #2980B9
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #EBF5FB
  BoxBackgroundColor #FEF9E7
  DividerBackgroundColor #FDEBD0
  GroupBorderColor #E74C3C
  GroupFontColor #C0392B
}

actor "사용자" as user
participant "run_poc.py" as entry
participant "config.py" as config
participant "graph_builder" as gb
participant "LangGraph\nRuntime" as lg
participant "generic_agent\n(node_fn)" as executor
participant "registry\n(lru_cache)" as registry
participant "prompt\nbuilder" as builder
participant "prompt\nloader" as loader
participant "llm_client\n(call_llm)" as llm
participant "routing" as router
participant "artifact\nparser" as parser
participant "LLM API\n(Google/Anthropic\n/OpenAI)" as api

== Phase 1: 부팅 및 설정 로딩 ==

user -> entry : python run_poc.py\n-p poc_classic.yaml\n-s "로또 번호 생성기"\n-o output/

note over entry, config #FFFDE7
  ① sys.path에 src/ 추가
  ② config.py 임포트 (모듈 로드 시점 자동 실행)
end note

entry -> config : import
activate config
config -> config : load_dotenv() → .env 읽기
config -> config : PROJECT_ROOT / ENGINE_DIR 등 경로 설정
config -> config : LLM_PROVIDER = "google" (기본값)
config -> config : MODEL = "gemini-2.5-flash"
config -> config : LLM_MAX_RETRIES = 2
config --> entry : 설정값 노출
deactivate config

note over entry #FFFDE7
  ③ setup_logging()
  ④ API 키 유효성 검증 (없으면 exit)
  ⑤ --user-story 읽기
end note

== Phase 2: 파이프라인 정의 로딩 ==

entry -> gb : load_pipeline_definition("poc_classic.yaml")
activate gb
note over gb #FFFDE7
  ⑥ YAML 읽기 → PipelineDefinition(**raw)
  PipelineDefinition(
    name="poc-classic", max_iterations=3,
    steps=[
      StepDefinition(step=1, agent="ReqAgent"),
      StepDefinition(step=2, agent="ValidatorAgent", on_fail="ReqAgent"),
      StepDefinition(step=3, agent="CodeAgent", max_tokens=16384),
    ]
  )
end note
gb --> entry : PipelineDefinition
deactivate gb

== Phase 3: 그래프 빌드 ==

entry -> gb : run_pipeline(pipeline_def, user_story)
activate gb

gb -> gb : PipelineState 초기화\n{user_story, steps_completed=[],\n latest_artifacts={}, iteration_count=0}

gb -> gb : build_graph_from_definition()

loop 각 step (1,2,3)마다
  gb -> executor : create_agent_node(step_def)
  activate executor

  executor -> registry : get_agent(agent_id)
  activate registry
  note over registry #FFFDE7
    최초 1회만 *.config.yaml 로드
    이후 lru_cache 캐싱 반환
  end note
  registry --> executor : AgentConfig
  deactivate registry

  executor -> builder : build_system_prompt(agent_config, step)
  activate builder
  note over builder #E8F5E9
    **System Prompt 조립 8단계**:
    1. Common Rules → load_common_prompt() → AgentCommon.txt
    2. Agent-specific Prompt → load_agent_prompt(agent_id)
    3. Output Templates (주출력 artifact 템플릿)
    4. [ValidatorAgent만] 5종 참조 템플릿
       (UC/TD/Impl/TR/FB — 스키마 검증용)
    5. [step.extra_templates 있으면] 추가 템플릿
    6. Constitution → load_constitution_excerpt()
    7. [ValidatorAgent만] _ADVERSARIAL_MANDATE 주입
       "fail 후보 3개 먼저 나열, BLOCKER 없을 때만 pass"
    8. [CodeAgent만] _CODE_FILE_MANDATE 주입
       "code_files 필드 필수, 완전한 코드 포함"
  end note

  builder -> loader : load_common_prompt()
  loader --> builder : AgentCommon.txt
  builder -> loader : load_agent_prompt(agent_id)
  loader --> builder : Agent별 .txt 프롬프트
  builder -> loader : load_template(name) [1~N회]
  loader --> builder : artifact 템플릿 YAML
  builder -> loader : load_constitution_excerpt()
  loader --> builder : constitution *.md
  builder --> executor : system_prompt (조립 완성)
  deactivate builder

  executor --> gb : node_fn 클로저 반환 (아직 미실행)
  deactivate executor

  gb -> gb : graph.add_node(node_id, node_fn)
end

note over gb #FFFDE7
  ⑮ step_1_ReqAgent → step_2_ValidatorAgent (단순 엣지)
  ⑯ step_2_ValidatorAgent → 조건부 엣지:
     make_validator_router(step_num=2, max_iterations=3)
     "pass" → step_3_CodeAgent
     "rework" → step_1_ReqAgent
     "max_retries" → END
  ⑰ step_3_CodeAgent → END (단순 엣지)
  ⑱ graph.compile()
end note

gb -> lg : compiled.invoke(initial_state)
activate lg

== Phase 4-1: ReqAgent 실행 (⑲~㉕) ==

lg -> executor : node_fn(state) [step_1_ReqAgent]
activate executor

executor -> executor : _build_user_message()\n→ ValidationReport 없음 → 최초 모드\n"[PMAgent] User Story를 분석하여 UC 작성..."

executor -> llm : call_llm(system_prompt, user_message)
activate llm

loop 품질 미달 retry (최대 max_retries=2회)
  llm -> api : _call_google(system, user_msg,\n  model="gemini-2.5-flash")
  api --> llm : LLMResponse(text=...)

  llm -> llm : _default_quality_check()\n(min_response_chars 검증)

  alt 품질 OK
    llm --> executor : LLMResponse
  else 품질 미달 or 429 rate-limit
    note over llm : 재시도 대기\n품질 미달: 즉시 재시도\n429: _extract_retry_delay() 후 대기
  end
end

deactivate llm

executor -> parser : extract_yaml_from_response(response.text)\n(```yaml 펜스 제거, artifact_id: 탐색)
parser --> executor : UseCaseModelArtifact YAML

executor -> executor : StepResult 생성\n{step_id, agent_id="ReqAgent",\n artifact_yaml, validation_result=None}

executor --> lg : state 업데이트\n{steps_completed+=[result],\n latest_artifacts["UC"]=yaml}
deactivate executor

== Phase 4-2: ValidatorAgent 실행 (㉖~㉛) ==

lg -> executor : node_fn(state) [step_2_ValidatorAgent]
activate executor

executor -> executor : _build_user_message()\n→ _find_validation_target() → "UseCaseModelArtifact"\n→ UC YAML만 전달! (context 격리)
note right of executor #FFE0E0
  **Context 격리 적용**:
  user_message = UC artifact YAML 만.
  ReqAgent의 system_prompt, 사고 과정 미포함.
end note

executor -> llm : call_llm(system_prompt,\n  uc_artifact_only)
activate llm
note over llm #E8F5E9
  system_prompt에 _ADVERSARIAL_MANDATE 포함:
  "List at least 3 potential failure candidates,
   state BLOCKER/NOT, pass only if ZERO blockers"
end note
llm -> api : _call_google(...)
api --> llm : ValidationReportArtifact 텍스트
llm --> executor : LLMResponse
deactivate llm

executor -> parser : extract_yaml_from_response()
executor -> parser : parse_artifact(artifact_yaml)
executor -> parser : get_validation_result(report_dict, raw_yaml)
parser --> executor : validation_result: "pass" | "warning" | "fail"

executor -> executor : validation_result in ("fail","warning")\n→ iteration_count += 1

executor --> lg : state 업데이트\n{validation_result, iteration_count}
deactivate executor

== Phase 4-3: 조건부 라우팅 (㉜) ==

lg -> router : route_after_validation(state)
activate router

alt validation_result == "pass"
  router --> lg : "pass" → step_3_CodeAgent 진행
else validation_result == "fail" or "warning"\nAND iteration_count < max_iterations (3)
  router --> lg : "rework" → step_1_ReqAgent 재실행
  note right : ⑲로 되돌아감\n_build_user_message() 재작업 모드:\n"ValidationReport + 이전 UC + User Story"
else validation_result == "fail" or "warning"\nAND iteration_count >= max_iterations
  router --> lg : "max_retries" → END
end

deactivate router

== Phase 4-4: CodeAgent 실행 (㉝~㉟, pass 후) ==

lg -> executor : node_fn(state) [step_3_CodeAgent]
activate executor

executor -> executor : _build_user_message() CodeAgent 분기\n→ "승인된 UC artifact 기반 Impl 작성\nUseCaseModelArtifact: ..."
note right of executor #E8F5E9
  system_prompt에 _CODE_FILE_MANDATE 포함:
  "code_files 필드 필수, 완전한 실행 코드"
end note

executor -> llm : call_llm(system_prompt, uc_yaml,\n  max_tokens=16384)
llm -> api : _call_google(...)
api --> llm : ImplementationArtifact YAML\n(code_files 포함)
llm --> executor : LLMResponse
executor -> parser : extract_yaml_from_response()
executor --> lg : state 업데이트 → END
deactivate executor

lg --> gb : final_state
deactivate lg

== Phase 5: 결과 저장 (㊱~㊲) ==

gb --> entry : final_state
deactivate gb

entry -> entry : pipeline_status 결정\niteration_count >= max_iterations?\n→ "max_retries_exceeded"\n그 외 → "completed"

entry -> parser : extract_artifact_id()\nextract_iteration()
note over entry #FFFDE7
  ㊱ steps_completed → iteration별 그룹화
  output/iteration-01/artifacts/
    001_UC-01.yaml
    002_UC-01-VAL-1.yaml
    003_IMPL-01.yaml
  ㊲ ImplementationArtifact → code_extractor
  output/workspace/ 에 실행 코드 저장
end note

entry -> entry : _save_artifacts(final_state, output/)
entry --> user : 완료 출력\n(artifacts 경로, 실행 명령어)

== 예외: Quota 소진 ==

note over entry, api #FFE0E0
  LLM API daily quota 소진 시:
  QuotaExhaustedError 발생
  → pipeline_status = "quota_exhausted"
  → 그때까지 생성된 partial artifacts는 저장 가능
end note

@enduml
